---
id: S02-T1-EnvConfig
title: Environment Configuration for Instances Path
status: pending
type: feature
requires:
  - NODE_EXPRESS
---

## Objective
Update the environment variables to dynamically point to the `totem/instances` directory rather than relying on relative paths which break depending on the execution context.

## Requirements
- Add `TOTEM_INSTANCES_PATH=../totem/instances` to `.env.example` and standard backend configuration.
- Ensure `server/src/index.ts` uses `process.env.TOTEM_INSTANCES_PATH` as a fallback or primary path instead of hardcoded `../../../`.
